Biography

Nath. W Dickerson, age 29 born Swanzey, mechanic, son of Nathaniel Dickerson, married on 11 Dec 1879 at the Baptist Church, Richmond, NH, to Alice M Ingalls, age 26 born Richmond, daughter of Isaac N Miller.[1]

Nathaniel William Dickinson was born on 9 March 1850 in Swanzey, New Hampshire. He was the son of Nathaniel Dickinson and Lucina Hill. He passed away, age 90y 10m 7d, at Richmond, NH, on 16 Jan 1941. His usual residence had been 5 Elm St., Winchester, NH, and his occupation had been a barber. His wife was Mary Alice Ingalls, age 87. He was buried on 19 Jan at Winchester, NH.[2]
